        <updateDate>2020-04-28T19:48:00Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>This bill requires the Department of Veterans Affairs to (1) expand the capabilities of the Women Veterans Call Center by including a text messaging capability, and (2) publish a website providing information for women veterans about the benefits and services available to them.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
